Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 至少阿兹派亚能守住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便我们倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一 也一定会赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定会拯救城池和民众
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会输给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太一他很强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早点告诉你该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你说 谢谢你能一直陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多希望至少能把那句话传达给他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己跟我说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:36.80,EP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1548,904)}第7话      召唤术师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总算来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我在地下收拾那群小鬼来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿再聊 护好她们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来决斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我的外挂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是能用物理攻击解决的对手好对付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一 你刚刚的强化是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不提升到这份上 根本没法好好打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米娅 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们三人 还有多少战力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话 不得不说情况很严峻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就能 勉强维持现状吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 这两个小孩是?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是小孩 是米洛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是小孩 是梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的帮手 她俩都是土系魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是咱们这一方的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看她们人小 本事可不小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我解决掉他们之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我守住后方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道你在跟谁说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 尽情地大显身手去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米洛也会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅洛也会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我说 真的很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一晚上就把那么多小鬼全清除了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,, 只能说这人已经是非人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才要实验嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂欢的收尾表演也已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟那位大人早已预料到了所有的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及所有的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不过是为帮其实现目的的棋子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是 你是 他们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对无法违背那位大人的意志的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真红魔物们在落叶魔术师释放战术级魔术后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分已失去战力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米娅终究还是发动了那一招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而疑似指挥官的真红食人鬼依旧毫发无损
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前正与赶去救援的少年交战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太一呢? 少年冒险者怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相上下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 应该说他发挥出的实力还要更高一筹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可毕竟是以一敌三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况还是不容乐观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜你就留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟其他冒险者一起保护阿兹派亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有把我当成工具 而是看作一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个女人来对待的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你的帮助 姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 外面还有那么多魔物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 你也要争口气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 只要能守住我们的城池
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点小伤不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双手染满了暗杀之血的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还可以重来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你太一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信愿意给予我信任的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.65,魔法咒语,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,972)}Thunder
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤莲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火炎波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.43,魔法咒语,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,984)}FallDown
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地陷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.93,魔法咒语,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(952,984)}FlameLance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰长矛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位姐姐 很厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就进入消耗战了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要浪费火力多动脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们要帮太一守好身后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强化到100 消耗果然很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该跟你说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定一只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米娅师父?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怎么会介入人类与魔物的争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地底的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双头龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,猊下 这难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 棋盘上所需的棋子总算都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的战斗才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自异世界的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我看看你有几分本事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 该不会是这场骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把沉睡在地底的龙给吵醒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他们很少离开自己的巢穴的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 在龙看来地面上的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟小虫子扇翅膀没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不足以让他们费心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可如今 对方却不知为何冒了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一 你该不会想跟龙打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说也太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可也不能临阵脱逃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是撒退战了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米娅师父 你带大家撤回城里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为防万一 做好避难准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你照顾好她们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要留下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初说好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会再让我一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 随你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那我就任性这一回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是俩不让师父省心的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个 要是擅自把命搞没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远都不原谅你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别插手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是几个意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该会是一场硬仗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一凛被当成冒标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会本能性地去保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候恐怕就真完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是要谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉安 你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上回果然是瞎猫碰上了死耗子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能硬碰硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在警告我不要插手?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙这种生物也太强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是蚂蚁对猛兽一般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可话又说回来了 刚刚那一击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要它想 完全可以对我造成致命伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要故意放水?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 它为什么要掺和到人类和魔物的争斗里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 你需要治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会 跑来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚不还在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不记得了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我绝对没有要给你拖后腿的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之这里很危险你赶紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜 安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜•史塔西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 别说了 乖乖待着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 都怪我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能活着就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着 我这就收拾好 带你去看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的…好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我当成一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当成一个女人来对待的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说能活着回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这份…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份心意一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的单相思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能让我…成为你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么傻话 咱们早就是朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我没保护好你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有我在 就不会让你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明保证过的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉反正自己有外挂 最后肯定能够化险为夷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管干什么 都得过且过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来 我什么也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么 一声不吭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就在那里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧来给我力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 要的就是这样强烈的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我也是无可奈何的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一 是驱使精灵的召唤术师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有施术者的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精灵是不能擅自动用力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是这个世界的理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能违反的戒律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可上回不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是特例
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太一自身的生命受到了威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是正式的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,契约?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,施术者命令精灵提供力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,施术者做好接受力量的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要缔结正式的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个条件缺一不可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然…是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不在你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能保护好安娜 责任在我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只怪我没有接受力量的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是很没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴上说着开挂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己就得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可内心却还留着胆怯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越人类的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:19:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀疑自己能不能用好这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这个世界应该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要能够保护大家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我力量艾莉安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命 我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后请称呼我为艾莉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你帮我看好她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我很重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛…我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为召唤术师了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉 你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一击结束战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了吾一记龙之咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还敢来挑战 胆量值得称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为高等种族的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要介入这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样 你才能不再插手这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 人族子孙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让吾看看 汝之真正实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,届时自然会回答汝之问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并离开此地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接这一招试试
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕你不成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妙哉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便回答 汝之提问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之所以介入这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃是受了某位大人之托
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的便是与汝一战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说清楚怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后给汝一个忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝接下来还会不接受那位大人的引导
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引导?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这对这个国家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃至这个世界而言都是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为赞同那位大人的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾才来帮一把手的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.23,0:22:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝切不可忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若想守护汝之珍宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就努力变强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.63,0:23:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 实验成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的那种力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年应是与风之精灵正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就得尽快开始下一项引导了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命 准备已在井然有序地进行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继城池之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就拿国家下手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集「王都惠内菲克斯」
